  "title": "feat(chat): add support for client side tools",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\nAdds client side tool support to React and JS.\r\n\r\nReact usage:\r\n```jsx\r\n<Chat\r\n  // ...\r\n  tools={[\r\n    type: 'tool-name',\r\n    component: () => <div>Tool Rendered</div>\r\n  ]}\r\n/>\r\n```\r\n\r\nJavascript usage:\r\n```javascript\r\nchat({\r\n  // ...\r\n  tools: [\r\n    {\r\n      type: 'tool-name',\r\n      template: {\r\n        component: (_, { html }) => html`<div>Tool rendered</div>`,\r\n      },\r\n    },\r\n  ],\r\n}),\r\n```",
